{"tid":2171958,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【歐洲動態】原來中國公安可在瑞士進行調查","createTime":"2020-08-24T09:53:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T10:29:40.000Z","uid":138409,"like":84,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"32ce10cb49aaec4f4bb0ee537f39d6b07f72c1aa","tid":2171958,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T09:53:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪要同瑞士施壓下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://europechinese.blogspot.com/2020/08/chcn.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feuropechinese.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F08%2Fchcn.html&d=aCvg504CNSeS5FxaNurzsqjPH3pfKCXBWMLigY0rPLs%3D&h=89d483b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://europechinese.blogspot.com/2020/08/chcn.html</a><br />\n<br />\n《星期日新蘇黎世報》（NZZ am Sonntag）昨天披露，原來瑞士跟中國2015年簽署了協議，瑞士准許中國公安在瑞士，對中國公民進行調查&mdash;&mdash;而這項協議<span class=\"gold\">從沒向瑞士國會或公眾披露，瑞中兩國目前正商討，把今年12月底到期的這項協議延長。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據協議，中國公安可在沒有「官方身份」下，在瑞士進行兩星期的調查，期間可盤問中國公民。協議的目的旨在打擊偷渡及逾期居留，如果中國公安發現了這類中國公民，需要遣返回中國，中國政府就會通知瑞士，在瑞士確認是可以遣返（例如不具備難民身份）後，這些人便要遣返。<br />\n瑞中兩國只正式根據這協議進行過一次遣返，是在2016年，涉及13人。<br />\n<br />\n這項協議被發現後，其中一個令一些瑞士議員不滿之處在於，<span class=\"gold\">瑞士政府從沒公佈。瑞士政府的解釋是，這項是「行政協議」，不是正式的國際條約，根據瑞士法例，不用正式刊憲。</span><br />\n<br />\n中國派員在海外執法，不是新聞，例如有歐洲城市邀請中國警察來巡邏，以協助遇到問題的中國遊客。而這類打擊偷渡的合作，也算正常。<br />\n<br />\n但問題出在：香港接連出現反修例及國安法爭議後，中國在西方的形象急速轉差，很難說服瑞士人中國不會借此來在瑞士跨境打壓中國公民（或來自中國的瑞士籍公民），或是在瑞士收集資料，用來在國內進行侵犯人權的行為。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">瑞士表示，當初簽署協議時，已表明協議不適用於西藏人和維吾爾族人。</span>但這個保證未必足以釋出疑慮。<br />\n<br />\n瑞士官員透露，瑞士跟大概60多個國家有這類協議。然而，其他國家可在瑞士執法的權限應該沒中國公安那麼大，是逐個個案跟瑞士討論，而非中國隨時可自己進行兩週調查。<br />\n<br />\n有國會的外交委員會成員被問及此事時，稱他都從未聽聞過這條協議。<span class=\"gold\">社會黨和綠黨議員已表示，反對延長這協議。</span><br />\n<br />\n相關報導：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.swissinfo.ch/eng/swiss-explore-renewal-of--secret-deal--with-china/45985878\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.swissinfo.ch%2Feng%2Fswiss-explore-renewal-of--secret-deal--with-china%2F45985878&d=aCvg504CNSeS5FxaNurzsqjPH3pfKCXBWMLigY0rPLs%3D&h=45b3f77a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.swissinfo.ch/eng/swiss-explore-renewal-of--secret-deal--with-china/45985878</a>"},{"pid":"24a08fb3c0844813a70cecf73da5920862ed0af2","tid":2171958,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T09:54:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"34a761b411973b6b4466a94136c6ed33787d31f2","tid":2171958,"uid":287461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T09:54:36.000Z","msg":"幫pushh<br />\n<br />\n精英級 國際戰線：&ldquo;Letters to the Editor&rdquo; 歡迎你！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fQeQqS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fQeQqS</a><br />\n&ldquo;Letters to the Editor&rdquo; 國際伺服器歡迎你！<br />\n誠邀各路英文精英，係外國報紙Letters版大展拳腳！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ae884fab203cf37d1179da637617137f3bb8752","tid":2171958,"uid":287461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T09:55:01.000Z","msg":"有冇得twitter？"},{"pid":"5da3435b576749f5b6791903da1cc558cb6b8968","tid":2171958,"uid":4840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T09:55:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f9f50b04236f57ef773e2375d06e9642d1db02b","tid":2171958,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T09:55:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7ce0ee34f85723be46ef7d73adce0d4456375aa8","tid":2171958,"uid":301503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T09:55:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2e1b6abf479d5426176cccd1f26e